{"tid":354396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴王舉報公屋鄰居貼揮春  房署：確可扣分","createTime":"2017-08-10T11:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T13:04:31.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c497623ed4e57301acb4e2e86b365db7ee6296","tid":354396,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"近日Facebook群組流傳一張電郵截圖，指<span style=\"color: red;\">有公屋住戶因在門外貼揮春而遭到投訴，投訴人更以「新年已過半年」為由，要求房署清除揮春。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貼文隨即惹起網民熱議，有人怒斥投訴者「係唔係都投訴」、「十分之霸道，貼揮春有甚麼問題，阻礙你嗎？」不過亦有網民指：「新公屋好似真係唔畀貼咁耐」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者佯裝租戶，致電政府1823熱線，聲稱想投訴屋邨鄰居貼揮春。無論記者提出的理由是「啲揮春搞到我周身唔聚財」、「邪住我呀」、或「搞到我風水唔好」，當<span style=\"color: red;\">值客戶服務主任均表示受理，並說：「你認為唔舒服就可以投訴」</span>。至於投訴能否成立，則待有關部門處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n房屋署回覆查詢時表示，一般情況下，不會要求租戶移除揮春等傳統習俗物品，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">若租戶將物品張貼於大廈公眾地方，例如走廊牆身，或物品造成阻礙</span>，房署或業主立案團則有權按房屋條例或大廈公契跟進。<span style=\"color: red;\">租戶如干犯「棄置雜物阻塞走廊或樓梯通道，妨礙清潔工作」，會被扣5分！<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2OyYjU6j0zvUgGuJsFAUwA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/252d21eb52d4014b6c2528291fec1fa8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2OyYjU6j0zvUgGuJsFAUwA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F252d21eb52d4014b6c2528291fec1fa8&h=b372d264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a613c2fe8c7a3552add3d589a19cfef19446f0a8","tid":354396,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"篤灰活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593757c81b3d2b29e73b3b6da1670781ac7806e4","tid":354396,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep